snippet.title: Johnny Depp trial: court played audio of actor asking Amber Heard to cut him
snippet.description:
Distressing audio in which Johnny Depp can be heard asking his ex-wife Amber Heard to "cut me" has been played in court as part of his libel trial.

Read up on last week's developments here: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/07/09/johnny-depp-attacked-ex-amber-heard-effectively-acting-nurse/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.
